	   <tr><td colspan=2>An Erudian Paladin would be an interesting combonation due to the fact that you don't see that combination used regularly (or often enough in game).&nbsp;&nbsp;People tend to use either a Human primarilly, however I play a Dwarve and I see Elf Paladian's as well.  You may want to consider boosting up the stats in both Strength and in Intelligence/Wisdom.  Stregnth will allow you to hit a little harder and intellignce/wisdom will allow you to learn new skills faster and it determines the amount of mana available to the character.  However I could be wrong, just my 2 cps.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dadin <br>54th Cavalier<br>Honored Circle on Xev<br><br>Dwarven Thane<br>Hellwinds - Palomides </td></tr>
