	   <tr><td colspan=2>The damage cap keeps you from doing maximum damage with your weapon until you are level 20.&nbsp;&nbsp;This is meant to keep twinked level 1's from doing more damage than first-time upper level players.  When you hit 20, at a damage of 25, you will start hitting close to 60 per hit.  Invest 1 point in double attack when you ding, and you will start to increase skill in it.  60 times 2 sounds good, doesn't it?  =)<br><br>Souldragoon Flamingheart<br>40th circle Paladin of Virtue<br>Fennin Ro<br>&nbsp;<br><i>Follow virtue, and the virtuous will follow you.</i></td></tr>
