	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ah, when i was lvl 25, i had just arrived in LoIO and got in a group immediatly, EXP WAS INCREDIBLE. Sarnaks are great exp, and ok loot. Personally i stayed there till 29, but you should till 27 i think. Than go to Frontier Mountains and hook up with a giant group, ok exp, GREAT LOOT. i stayed there till 32, 33 is good too. Than i went to unrest and got into a ghost group at lvl 33. INCREDIBLE EXP PLUS GREAT LOOT. also, you WILL make a lot of friends here if you go, ppl tend to saty in zone for 10+ hours in 2 or so days. Drops are FS weapons usually, Jagged bands occasionally, DWB's RARELY, words runes and cash almost always, Bronze armor sometimes. at lvl 35, i suggest staying in Unrest, but soloing at the blood pool. If you have a wurm, this isnt too risky, but with a ghoulbane, it is. GREAT EXP. Next Step, Velious or LOWER GUK. LGuk is pretty decent exp, but dangerous hehe. drops are GREAT. FS weapons, words runes, cash, RARE GOOD DROPS. first group i got into at lvl 36 was the ghoul supplier. stayed there for 4 hours, hit 37 at the end of the 3rd, got a Thick banded belt( ac 8, str+15!!!!!!, worth 10+k) at the end of the 4th. So, you may want to follow this guide or not, your choice. (Consider the amount of time it took me to type this and how numb my fingers are right now)<br>Just my crazy 2cp<br>Zomor Soulsaver-bertoxx<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
